high_descs: Turn around and walk to the long brown counter across the room to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the knife on the counter that is between you and the bread.
Turn around and go across the room to the sink on your right.
Slice the tomato that is sitting next to the sink.
Turn to the left and go across the room to the microwave on your left.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn left and go across the room to the sink on your left.
Pick up a slice of the tomato.
Turn to the left and go across the room to the microwave on your left.
Put the tomato slice into the microwave, cook it and then take it back out.
Turn around a go across the room to the trash can on your right.
Throw the tomato slice into the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw a cooked tomato slice into the trash can.

high_descs: Walk to the left of the table and then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Walk around the kitchen and turn right to face the tomato on the sink.
Cut the tomato into slices.
Walk to the opposite corner of the room and turn left to face the microwave at the end of the counter.
Put the knife into the microwave and close it.
Walk to the opposite corner of the room and face the tomato on the sink.
Pick up a slice of the tomato on the edge of the sink.
Walk to the opposite corner of the room to face the microwave on the counter.
Heat the slice of tomato in the microwave and remove it.
Turn around, walk across the room and turn right to face the trash can.
Put the tomato slice into the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Cut a slice of tomato, heat it, as well as put the tomato slice in the trash can.

high_descs: Move to the kitchen island counter top where the loaf of bread is
Pickup the knife with green handle by the bread
Move to the kitchen sink
Slice the tomato in front of the sink
Turn around and go directly to the microwave
open the microwave and put the knife next to the apple inside and shut the door
Go back to the sink where the rest of the tomato is
Grab a slice of the tomato
Take the tomato slice back to the microwave
Open the door and place the slice inside, turn on the microwave then open the door
Take only the tomato slice out and move to the grey trash bin
Throw the tomato slice in the trash
anns.task_desc: Cook a tomato slice to throw away in the trash

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the counter with the sponge.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Walk over to the sink.
Slice the tomato with the knife.
Turn around and walk over to the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the knife inside then close the microwave.
Walk back over to the kitchen sink.
Pick up one slice of tomato.
Walk back over to the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the tomato inside, then close the microwave and turn it on. In a few seconds, turn the microwave off and open it. Take the tomato out.
Walk over to the trash can on the other side of the kitchen.
Put the tomato in the trash.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot piece slice of tomato microwaved with a knife inside the trash can.

high_descs: Turn around walk towards fridge, turn right, turn left walk to counter with green sponge.
Pick up knife in front of bread.
Turn left, walk towards door, turn left walk to the sink.
Cut the tomato into slices with the knife.
Turn left, turn left, walk to microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Go back to the tomato.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Go back to microwave with the tomato.
Put the tomato in the microwave and cook it.
Retrieve the tomato from the microwave.
Put the tomato slice in the gray trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put the knife and tomato slice in the microwave, throw the tomato slice away.
